725882f-a.title: Queens: 147th Street - 10th Avenue
725882f-a.text:
147th Street, north from 10th Avenue, Whitestone. The land
on the left was owned(in 1891) by E. Powell, and that on the
right by S. Overton Douglass.
P. L. Sperr  March 5, 1932

724995f-a.title: Queens: 10th Avenue - 147th Street
724995f-a.text:
10th Avenue (right), at the N.E. corner of 147th Street,
showing a frame house with watch tower, popular in t he second
half of the nineteenth century. At was owned by W. S. Overton
Douglass in 1891 and by George B. Douglas in 1909. The house
on the right was owned by O'Brien.
P. L. Sperr  March 5, 1932
